==Tailoring==
Wild Horseradish is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a {{name|Shirt008|link=Tailoring{{!}}"Good Grief" Shirt|class=inline}}. It is a brown dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the orange dye pot at Emily's and Haley's house for use in [[dyeing]].

==Quests==
*Wild Horseradish may be randomly requested during [[Spring]] at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|150}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.

==History==
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].  Added Shrimp Cocktail recipe.}}

